#

Beef Borscht with Sour Cream

105 min
$15.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

high-proteinlow-carb

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Main

Tags:

soupheartybeetbeef

Description

A hearty and vibrant beet soup enriched with tender beef, served with a dollop of tangy sour cream.

Ingredients

  • beef stew meat: 1 lb
  • beets: 3 medium
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • potatoes: 2 medium, diced
  • carrots: 2 medium, sliced
  • onion: 1 large, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • beef broth: 6 cups
  • sour cream: 1 cup
  • vegetable oil: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh dill: for garnish, optional
